NAME

DateTime::Locale::ig - Locale data examples for the Igbo (ig) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Igbo locale.

Date Formats

Full 

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Tiuzdee, 5 Febrụwarị 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Fraịdee, 22 Disemba 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Satọdee, 15 Septemba -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Febrụwarị 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Disemba 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Septemba -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Feb 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Dis 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Sep -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5/2/08
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/95
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/9/-10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Febrụwarị 2008 na 18:30:30 UTC
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Disemba 1995 na 09:05:02 UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Septemba -10 na 04:44:23 UTC

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Feb 2008, 18:30:30
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Dis 1995, 09:05:02
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Sep -10, 04:44:23

  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/9/-10, 04:44
